      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/dc35c4f0-8588-11e2-926e-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
